    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "14 November, 1953",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "15th Cml.Tech.Intel.Det.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "100th Cml.Grp.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Fort McClellan, Alabama",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Smith,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Your letter was recieved Nov. 12, 1953. Thank you very much",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "for replying and offering your aid. We also wish to thank Mrs. Bou-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "cher.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "As you will notice my address has changed. Until further",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "notice it will be as shown in the upper right hand corner.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "At the present time our research activities are being kept",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "secret. However, at a time in the future when we have no need to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "use this security measure, I will personally write and inform you",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "of what we were and possibly are doing. Our research does have a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "connection with the \"flying saucer\", although it is at present a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "secondary issue. The main body of our research is with electric",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "fields. (It is not a \"copy\" of what Keyhoe mentioned in his recent",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "book relating to the Canadian Project. The research with which we",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "are concered has been carried on for many years now by a research",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "foundation in Western United States-which is not connected to us.)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "The \"flying saucer\" reports are of value to us because they may",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "give clues toward the investigation of various phases in our re-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "search.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "I have told you these things so that you might understand",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "the need for our recieving saucer reports; also because you are no",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "doubt curious about our activities. (Every once in a while I will",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "inform you of our activity.) Because you and Mrs. Boucher are taking",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "the time and trouble to help us - in turn, we wish to cooperate as",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "best we can to in some way return the favor. So, do not hesitate in",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "calling on us in the future.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Yours truly,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Charles A. Yost",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Coordinator",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "OC Research Laboratory, in",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "St. Clair Shores, Michigan",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "E-1",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    }
  ],
